    "en": {
      "title": "Harak Kata\u2019s drug peddler \u2019Kudu Batti\u2019 arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The STF has arrested two suspects including a woman known as 'Kudu Batti' who are accomplices of the notorious drug kingpin and the leader of an organized criminal gang Nadun Chinthaka alias 'Harak Kata'.",
        "STF said the 40-year-old woman and a 34-year-old man who are residents of Rajagiriya and Tangalle were arrested with 51g of heroin during a raid in Rajagiriya.",
        "Investigations revealed the suspects were distributing heroin under the influence of 'Harak Kata'."
